org.zephyr.data

Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zephyr.data.Record
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Entry>

    public class Record
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Entry>
    An record of data that contains 0..N Entries, in order, and provides accessor methods to them. It has an identifier that will be generated for it if one is not provided to it.
